//MARK: About View
"aboutView_aboutSection" = "Developer Notes";
"aboutView_linksSection" = "Links";
"aboutView_aboutText" = "**Made with ❤️ by Adi Ben-Dahan in Tel Aviv 🇮🇱**\n\nThis project started as a personal quest for a messaging tool that truly respected privacy.\n\nNo clouds.\nNo analytics.\nNo silent observers.\n\nJust a fast, reliable filter running entirely on your device with nothing that leaves your hands.\nAnd since many tools in this space sit behind a subscription or paywall, I thought it’d be nice to have a version that just works with no strings attached. This app is **free** to use, and it will **stay free**.\n\n**I'll be very happy to recieve five star rating on the AppStore ⭐️❤️.**\n\nIf something feels off or isn’t behaving as expected, a quick note on the GitHub issues page or an email is always appreciated.";
